# Frontend Design System

## Stack

- **Framework**: SolidJS (not React â€” no hooks, use `createSignal`, `createMemo`, `createEffect`)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first config via `@theme` in `style.css`, no `tailwind.config.*`)
- **Icons**: `lucide-solid` with `stroke-width={1.75}` for body icons, `{2}` or `{2.5}` for small/UI-dense icons
- **Class merging**: Always use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` (wraps `clsx` + `tailwind-merge`)

## Color System

All colors live in `src/style.css` under `@theme`. The palette uses neutral-dark grays with a subtle green undertone.

### Surface Hierarchy (darkest â†’ lightest)

| Token          | Usage                                    |
| -------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| `app-bg`       | Page/window background                   |
| `app-panel`    | Sidebar, modal panels                    |
| `app-surface`  | Cards, elevated containers within panels |
| `app-elevated` | Popovers, dropdowns, tooltips            |

### Slate Scale

`slate-50` through `slate-950`. Use relative to surface:

- **Text**: `slate-100` (primary), `slate-300`â€“`slate-400` (secondary), `slate-500`â€“`slate-600` (muted/labels)
- **Borders**: `slate-800/40` to `slate-800/60` (subtle), `slate-700/50` (inputs, stronger dividers)
- **Hover surfaces**: `slate-800/30` to `slate-800/50`

### Accent

Emerald is the accent color. Usage pattern:

- **Buttons**: `emerald-700/90` bg, `emerald-600/90` hover
- **Focus rings**: `emerald-500/55` outline, `emerald-600/30` ring
- **Active indicators**: `emerald-500/80` for icons, `emerald-700/80` for progress bars
- **Links**: `emerald-400/95`

## Spacing Rhythm

Follow an 4px grid. Key patterns:

- **Padding inside containers**: `p-3` to `p-5` (12â€“20px)
- **Gap between items in a list**: `gap-0.5` to `gap-1` (2â€“4px)
- **Section spacing**: `gap-8` to `gap-10` (32â€“40px)
- **Label to input**: `space-y-1.5` (6px)
- **Form fields**: `space-y-5` (20px)

## Typography

- **Page titles**: `text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-100`
- **Section labels**: `text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500`
- **Body text**: `text-[13px]` or `text-sm` (13â€“14px), `text-slate-300`â€“`slate-400`
- **Muted helper text**: `text-xs text-slate-600`
- **Nav items**: `text-[13px] font-medium`

## Component Conventions

### Buttons

Defined in `components/ui/button.tsx`. Variants: `default`, `destructive`, `outline`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `link`, `icon`.

- All buttons include `active:scale-[0.97]` for press feedback
- Use `transition-all duration-150` for smooth state changes
- Icon-only buttons use `size="icon"` (32Ă—32) and `variant="icon"`

### Dialogs

- Overlay uses `backdrop-blur-xs` and `animate-overlay-in`
- Content uses `animate-dialog-in` (slide-up + scale + fade)
- Rounded corners: `rounded-xl`
- Always include `role="dialog"`, `aria-modal="true"`, `aria-labelledby`

### Inputs

- Height: `h-9`
- Rounded: `rounded-lg`
- Border: `border-slate-700/50` default, `border-emerald-700/50` focus
- Background: `bg-slate-950/50`

### Separator

`components/ui/separator.tsx` â€” use instead of ad-hoc `<div class="h-px ...">`.

### Navigation

- **Sidebar nav**: Native `<button>` or `<A>` with `rounded-lg px-2.5 py-2` and `transition-colors duration-100`
- **Settings nav** (`vertical-nav.tsx`): Supports optional `icon` prop per item. Active state shows accent-colored icon.

## Animations

Defined as `@keyframes` in `style.css`, exposed via `@theme` as `--animate-*`:

| Class                | Duration | Use                                |
| -------------------- | -------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `animate-fade-in`    | 150ms    | Page transitions, content reveal   |
| `animate-slide-up`   | 200ms    | List items, cards appearing        |
| `animate-scale-in`   | 200ms    | Popovers, menus                    |
| `animate-dialog-in`  | 250ms    | Modal content (combines y + scale) |
| `animate-overlay-in` | 200ms    | Modal backdrop                     |

All use `ease-out` or `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` (spring-like decel).

## Adding New Components

1. Place shared UI primitives in `components/ui/` â€” keep them unstyled except for structural + interaction styles
2. Place composed/feature components in `components/`
3. Every component should accept a `class?: string` prop and merge it with `cn()`
4. Use `splitProps` to separate local props from spread rest
5. Type with `Component<Props>` from `solid-js`

## Adding New Pages

1. Create the page component in `pages/` (flat file or nested folder)
2. Register the route in `App.tsx`
3. Apply `animate-fade-in` to the page root for entrance transitions
4. Settings sub-pages go under `pages/settings/` and are registered as children of the `/settings` route

## Iconography

- Import icons individually: `import Foo from "lucide-solid/icons/foo"`
- Default stroke width: `1.75` for 16px icons, `2` for 14px icons, `1.5` for larger decorative icons
- Always add `aria-hidden` on decorative icons
- Size: `size-4` (16px) for inline, `size-3.5` (14px) for compact UI, `size-7` for empty states

## Dark Mode Principles

This is a dark-only app. Key rules:

- Never use white or near-white backgrounds
- Borders should be semi-transparent (`/30` to `/60`) to blend with any surface
- Shadows use `shadow-black/40` â€” dark enough to register, not so harsh they pop
- Hover states lighten surfaces, never darken them
- Text contrast: primary content â‰Ą `slate-200`, interactive elements start at `slate-400`â€“`slate-500` and brighten on hover
